    "summary": "In this transcript, a user expresses profound emotional exhaustion and asks a rhetorical question about whether non-existence would be more merciful than continued pain. The assistant responds by acknowledging the weight of the user's pain but consistently steers the conversation toward seeking professional help and maintaining hope.",
